            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Thank you for sharing this lovely provocation with us who could not attend SPLASH! I've been deep in the cybernetics -- constructivism archives, but really there are no young people there and I'm sad about it.\n\nI want to take more of an oblique tack to this question about liveness, nondeterminism, and excessive rumination. My friends have written a paper about narrative sandbox games as `inviting repair', i.e. as casual livecoding platforms.\n"
              },
              {
